com.nexmo.client.insight

Class InsightClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nexmo.client.insight.InsightClient

  • public class InsightClient
extends java.lang.Object
    A client for talking to the Nexmo Number Insight API. The standard way to obtain an instance of this class is to use NexmoClient.getInsightClient().
